{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/resources/buy-bitcoin/","result":{"data":{"resourcesJson":{"page":"/resources/buy-bitcoin/","title":"Buy Bitcoin","lead":"Where to easily buy bitcoin.","description":"There are many ways to buy bitcoin, but not all methods are equal. Some require KYC while others may not allow you withdrawal your funds. Learn which are the most reputable.","body":"<p>While some KYC exchanges are listed, it is best to avoid them. Consider your needs when choosing where to buy your bitcoin.</p><ul  class='list'><li><strong>Available</strong>: Countries in which the option is available.</li><li><strong>KYC</strong>: <b>K</b>now <b>Y</b>our <b>C</b>ustomer (KYC) is the practice of verifying the identity of clients. You should place a high priority on privacy, and avoid buying bitcoin that requires KYC, as it means your identity is tied to your purchases and to the wallet addresses where that bitcoin is kept. Data leaks, which happen often, can put you and your bitcoin at risk.</li><li><strong>Bitcoin Only</strong>: Services that focus on Bitcoin only tend to provide a better experience and tend to have a smaller attack surface.</li><li><strong>Keys</strong>: Not your keys, not your coins. Select methods that deposit directly to your wallet, or allow withdrawal.</li><li><strong>Additonal Info</strong>: More information on the service.</li></ul>","cardType":"extended","lastUpdate":"16 January 2023","links":[{"title":"Peach","url":"https://peachbitcoin.com","description":"Peach is a mobile application that connects Bitcoin Buyers & Sellers together.<br><strong>Referral code: PR9D17</strong>","pills":null,"details":[{"label":"Available","description":"Switzerland, Europe","category":"grey"},{"label":"KYC","description":"No","category":"green"},{"label":"Bitcoin Only","description":"Yes","category":"green"},{"label":"Keys","description":"Deposit to Address","category":"green"},{"label":"Additional Info","description":"NA","ca